				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-T%E1%BB%AD-Huy/Bi%E1%BB%87n-Kinh-k%E1%BB%B7-s%E1%BB%B1-k%E1%BB%B3-17/poem-hLZfm0_Xg7Hnl_1wWpNmsQ">Biện Kinh kỷ sự kỳ 17 - 汴京紀事其十七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-T%E1%BB%AD-Huy/author-EtcdSnyLUXRLONaaTmRisQ">Lưu Tử Huy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/B%E1%BB%93-t%C3%A1t-man-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-B%C3%A1ch-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Ba/poem-2IvRgP1KSGX-VTspk_iXZA">Bồ tát man - Đại Bách Địa - 菩薩蠻－大柏地</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/author-h4yM6-N0eITEQqfS6Lh1ag">Mao Trạch Đông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Cung-trung-h%C3%A0nh-l%E1%BA%A1c-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-rA1CLISRBjgqgv3dUmhbjg">Cung trung hành lạc kỳ 1 - 宮中行樂其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/H%E1%BB%93ng-H%C3%A0-thu%E1%BB%B7-quy%E1%BA%BFt/poem-Rx5uFr8STIygSw1TM9Rw_A">Hồng Hà thuỷ quyết - 紅河水決</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-k7nDOMHcGKaZoky6ue8-ag">Nguyễn Thượng Hiền</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%AFc/T%C3%A0m-ph%E1%BB%A5-ng%C3%A2m/poem-2to2RMksKQSzoVIkl7LRrg">Tàm phụ ngâm - 蠶婦吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%AFc/author-drmUP7dwRTnFglgIqZwgrw">Tạ Phương Đắc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-ca-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u/poem--c5sKgn5KP6ERkqm_L3H5g">Thuỷ điệu ca đầu - 水調歌頭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/author-wRpSKwqTcKjFpinJIe2YPg">Hoàng Đình Kiên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E